<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.5.1">
<l>vīṟṟirun tēḻulakun taṉikkōl cella vīvilcīr</l>
<l>āṟṟaṉmik kāḷu mammāṉaivemmā piḷantāṉṟaṉṉai</l>
<l>pōṟṟi yeṉṟē kaikaḷārat toḻutu coṉmālaikaḷ</l>
<l>ēṟṟa nōṟṟēṟ kiṉiyeṉṉakuṟai yeḻumaiyumē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>“The lord who rules, sitting in distinction, abounding in power with imperishable excellence</l>
<l>while [his] sovereignity goes over the seven worlds, the one who tore the mouth of the cruel horse,</l>
<l>praise [to him],” to me who has done penance who, so saying, [my] hands fully worshipping,</l>
<l>raised a word garland, what want will now be there in seven birth?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
